title: Deck Builder
description: A deck building application that allows users to search for cards and add them to their deck. Users can also create an account, save their decks, and view other users decks.

title: Collection Tracker
description: A collection tracker application that allows users to search for cards and add them to their collection. Users can also create an account, save their collection, and view other users collections.

title: Store
description: A store application that allows users to search for cards and add them to their cart. Users can also create an account, save their cart, and view other users carts.
